The '''Jrade-Daders Concourse''' was a concourse on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. In [[21 BBY/Legends|21 BBY]], an [[SAGroup (COMPOR)/Legends|SAGroup]] rally marched from there to [[Monument Plaza/Legends|Monument Plaza]].

